  "intro": "<p>  </p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: -29.1px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" sc\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(148,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 146);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures\">微光-橙光《真实幻象》主题曲</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: -29.1px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" sc\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(148,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 146);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures\">作品链接：<a href=\"http://www.66rpg.com/game/717061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">http://www.66rpg.com/game/717061</a></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: -29.1px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" sc\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(148,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 146);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures\">作品简介：</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: -29.1px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" sc\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(148,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 146);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures\">针对当下年轻人最常见和最有可能遭遇的骗局，</span><span style=\"text-indent: -29.1px;\">选取真实新闻事情件，进行虚构创作，以达到娱乐和警示的目的。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: -29.1px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" sc\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(148,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 146);\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures\">刚入职的女实习记者季哲，接到北国大学女生薛笙的爆料，称上厕所时被人偷拍。季哲前去采访，校方担心影响声誉并不配合调查，未抓到偷拍者，此事不了了之。对偷拍深恶痛绝的季哲不愿轻易放弃，打算继续追踪。却在此时传来国大女生跳楼案，警方判定为自杀，但季哲凭借敏锐的洞察力，觉得此事并不简单，她在深挖故事真相的同时，意外唤醒了潜藏多年的超能力。季哲使用超能力，找出了令人痛心的自杀真相。就在此时，国大又传来死讯，这次的死者是国大校花…</span></p>\n <span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures\"><br>\n </span>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
